Desireé Cousteau https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Desire%C3%A9_Cousteau 0 Desireé Cousteau was the stage name of a former pornographic actress of the 1970s and 1980s. She is best known for her roles in the 1978 film Pretty Peaches and 1979's Inside Désirée Cousteau. In 1993, she was inducted into the XRCO Hall of Fame, and, in 1997, she was inducted into the AVN Hall of Fame.
